# Engine Refactor — Implementation Plan

Decompose the 3,368-line [bot.rs](file:///c:/Users/mehul/OneDrive/Desktop/Studio/PROJECTS/polycli/polycli/src/commands/bot.rs) into focused engine modules, then layer on gatekeeper, event logging, WebSocket feed, and event-by-event replay — carrying forward the best architecture ideas from `boooot_compare_2`.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Each phase is a standalone, compilable checkpoint. We never break `cargo build` or `cargo test` mid-phase.

---

