## Phase 7: Event-by-Event Backtest Replay

**Goal:** True historical replay at event granularity.

### [NEW] [replay.rs](file:///c:/Users/mehul/OneDrive/Desktop/Studio/PROJECTS/polycli/polycli/src/bot/replay.rs)

```rust
pub enum ReplayMode {
    EventByEvent,
    LiveParity1s,
}
```

Implement `StrategyInputSource` for parquet row iteration. Same strategy runner handles both live and replay.

