- `gatekeeper_allows_normal_entry`
- `gatekeeper_emergency_halt_blocks_all`
- `gatekeeper_cooldown_blocks_then_expires`

### Build Verification

```powershell
# Full release build — must succeed
cargo build --release 2>&1
```

### Functional Smoke Test (after Phases 1-3)

```powershell
# Verify CLI still works — should print help
cargo run -- bot --help
```

```powershell
# Verify list-markets works (no wallet needed)
cargo run -- bot list-markets --input pmxtarchives --crypto btc --limit 3
```
